		"excerpt": "This app started with a casual request on Tuesday, March 27th, in a public CloudFlare support thread. \"I think it would be great if CloudFlare had an app to aid in Earth Hour this upcoming Saturday, March 31 @ 8:30 PM. It's not too late to join in on the effort!\"",
		"feature_image": "https://cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/zkvhlag99gkb/6pCOCHoEr4tKhLcPcHsjt6/46e5d3922deb7e1d1ceaeba9e29ad371/app-observe-earth-hour-on-your-website.png",
		"featured": false,
		"html": "<p></p>\n    <div class=\"flex anchor relative\">\n      <h3 id=\"it-would-be-great-if\">&quot;It would be great if...&quot;</h3>\n      <a href=\"#it-would-be-great-if\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"relative sm:absolute sm:-start-5\">\n        <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentcolor\" d=\"m12.11 15.39-3.88 3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1-3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0-3.5l3.88-3.88a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-3.88 3.89a4.48 4.48 0 0 0 6.33 6.33l3.89-3.88a1 1 0 1 0-1.42-1.42Zm8.58-12.08a4.49 4.49 0 0 0-6.33 0l-3.89 3.88a1 1 0 0 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1 3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0 3.5l-3.88 3.88a1 1 0 1 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.89a4.49 4.49 0 0 0 0-6.33ZM8.83 15.17a1 1 0 0 0 1.1.22 1 1 0 0 0 .32-.22l4.92-4.92a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-4.92 4.92a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.42Z\"></path></svg>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n    <p>This app started with a casual request on Tuesday, March 27th, in a public CloudFlare support thread.</p><blockquote><p>I think it would be great if CloudFlare had an app to aid in Earth Hour this upcoming Saturday, March 31 @ 8:30 PM. It&#39;s not too late to join in on the effort!</p></blockquote><p>Time was too short for CloudFlare to help, based on other projects. But — just in case — I mentioned the alpha version of our developer platform. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/C19H34O2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Katie G.</a>, a developer in the UK, warned that she was busy with lots of work and other projects, but ended with:</p><blockquote><p>I&#39;ll still try to do it though in time for Earth Hour.</p></blockquote>\n    <div class=\"flex anchor relative\">\n      <h3 id=\"underpromise-overdeliver\">Underpromise, Overdeliver</h3>\n      <a href=\"#underpromise-overdeliver\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"relative sm:absolute sm:-start-5\">\n        <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentcolor\" d=\"m12.11 15.39-3.88 3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1-3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0-3.5l3.88-3.88a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-3.88 3.89a4.48 4.48 0 0 0 6.33 6.33l3.89-3.88a1 1 0 1 0-1.42-1.42Zm8.58-12.08a4.49 4.49 0 0 0-6.33 0l-3.89 3.88a1 1 0 0 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1 3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0 3.5l-3.88 3.88a1 1 0 1 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.89a4.49 4.49 0 0 0 0-6.33ZM8.83 15.17a1 1 0 0 0 1.1.22 1 1 0 0 0 .32-.22l4.92-4.92a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-4.92 4.92a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.42Z\"></path></svg>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n    <p>Last night — about 48 hours later — <a href=\"https://www.cloudflare.com/apps/earthhour\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Earth Hour</a> was made available to all CloudFlare customers as a free CloudFlare app!</p><p>Turn on <a href=\"https://www.cloudflare.com/apps/earthhour\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">the app</a>, and for one hour on March 31 (today, for some; tomorrow for many) your site will go dark and present a message to the site visitor explaining <a href=\"http://www.earthhour.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Earth Hour</a>. The app offers site owners the chance to &quot;Save the world, 60 minutes every 365 days at a time.&quot;</p><p>We applaud Katie for her quick work, and her questions during development have helped us improve the platform already.</p>\n    <div class=\"flex anchor relative\">\n      <h3 id=\"what-can-you-do-on-cloudflare\">What Can You Do On CloudFlare?</h3>\n      <a href=\"#what-can-you-do-on-cloudflare\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"relative sm:absolute sm:-start-5\">\n        <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentcolor\" d=\"m12.11 15.39-3.88 3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1-3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0-3.5l3.88-3.88a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-3.88 3.89a4.48 4.48 0 0 0 6.33 6.33l3.89-3.88a1 1 0 1 0-1.42-1.42Zm8.58-12.08a4.49 4.49 0 0 0-6.33 0l-3.89 3.88a1 1 0 0 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1 3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0 3.5l-3.88 3.88a1 1 0 1 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.89a4.49 4.49 0 0 0 0-6.33ZM8.83 15.17a1 1 0 0 0 1.1.22 1 1 0 0 0 .32-.22l4.92-4.92a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-4.92 4.92a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.42Z\"></path></svg>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n    <p>More info coming soon about this developer platform. But the impatient can follow links in this <a href=\"http://support.cloudflare.com/discussions/suggestions/1168-earth-hour\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">thread</a>. If you&#39;d like to develop an app, <a href=\"http://support.cloudflare.com/discussion/new\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">let us know</a>. Developers can build globally-deployable apps for CloudFlare-powered sites, with no operation costs, to join the existing <a href=\"https://www.cloudflare.com/apps\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">CloudFlare apps</a>. That&#39;s just the beginning.</p>\n    <div class=\"flex anchor relative\">\n      <h3 id=\"dont-forget\">Don&#39;t Forget</h3>\n      <a href=\"#dont-forget\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"relative sm:absolute sm:-start-5\">\n        <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentcolor\" d=\"m12.11 15.39-3.88 3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1-3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0-3.5l3.88-3.88a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-3.88 3.89a4.48 4.48 0 0 0 6.33 6.33l3.89-3.88a1 1 0 1 0-1.42-1.42Zm8.58-12.08a4.49 4.49 0 0 0-6.33 0l-3.89 3.88a1 1 0 0 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1 3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0 3.5l-3.88 3.88a1 1 0 1 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.89a4.49 4.49 0 0 0 0-6.33ZM8.83 15.17a1 1 0 0 0 1.1.22 1 1 0 0 0 .32-.22l4.92-4.92a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-4.92 4.92a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.42Z\"></path></svg>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n    <p>It&#39;s easy to observe <a href=\"https://www.cloudflare.com/apps/earthhour\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Earth Hour</a>, no matter your time zone.</p>",
